high_descs: Turn right and walk to the stove.

Turn right and walk to the sink.
Rinse the kettle in the sink and then pick the washed kettle up from the sink.
Turn around and walk to the brown shelf across from the brown door.
Place the kettle on the second shelf from the bottom.
